creator: Kongregate
descriptionHtml:
Become a studio tycoon at Tap Tap Studios. Film new shows & movies in this fun idle clicker game. Click your way to stardom and fortune! Train your showrunner and build a cinema empire. Hire celebrities and lead the development of projects from concept to pilot. Curtains up! It’s showtime at Tap Tap Studios.

Features
Build!
Create your own studio empire from pilot to production, one hit at a time.


Hire a Crew
Get in the action with the best crew & assistants and start making movies like a pro!

Scout Locations
Unlock epic movie sets for your next project.

Action!
Film the next streaming hit show or movie using iconic Hollywood celebrities.

Make Money
Click your way to stardom and success.
